title: 2021 March Madness Special
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico are in studio for a March Madness preview. Rico gives out the Wilson ball matchups, Dave fills out his bracket and spreads don't matter!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
